channel.description:

Also I got another problem, When barraging [Not using autocast] If you click barrage on him too fast or don't time it right you'll run up to your target then barrage or just sit their by him, I need to make it so you can farcast w/o ancient staff. Also if someone is running and you barrage them sometimes they can keep running even though you hit them with barrage 2-3 times. Any help is appreciated!
-Unleashed
